---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Starter Config Templates — changelogs.info" description="Copy-paste starter configs for popular AI coding tools.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Starter Configs</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-text-secondary">Use these as baseline templates and tune for your project.</p>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-8">
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card p-5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">CLAUDE.md</h2>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 text-sm"><code># Project Conventions

- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Write tests for all new features
- Keep commits small and atomic
- Prefer functions over classes where possible
- Never commit secrets
</code></pre>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card p-5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">.cursorrules</h2>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 text-sm"><code>You are working in a TypeScript monorepo.
- Keep changes minimal and focused
- Add/update tests for behavior changes
- Prefer existing project patterns
- Run lint + typecheck before finishing
</code></pre>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card p-5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">.aider.conf.yml</h2>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 text-sm"><code>model: sonnet
auto-commits: true
pretty: true
gitignore: true
</code></pre>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-xl border border-border bg-bg-card p-5">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">.continue/config.json</h2>
        <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-bg-tertiary p-4 text-sm"><code>&#123;
  "models": [
    &#123; "title": "Claude Sonnet", "provider": "anthropic", "model": "claude-sonnet-4-5" &#125;
  ],
  "tabAutocompleteModel": &#123; "provider": "ollama", "model": "qwen2.5-coder:7b" &#125;
&#125;
</code></pre>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
